== 荣誉 ==
{{see also|湯姆·漢克獲獎列表}}
[[File:Tom_Hanks_-_footprint.JPG|thumb]]
湯·漢斯因为《[[費城_(電影)|費城]]》（1993）、《[[阿甘正傳|阿甘正傳]]》（1994）曾接连2届赢得了[[奥斯卡最佳男主角奖|奥斯卡最佳男主角奖]]。他的电影《阿甘正传》感动了全球很多人，也让很多人相信美国梦和向往美国。
他以46岁年紀成為最年轻获得[[美國電影學會|美國電影學會]]终身成就奖的演员。

2016年11月，湯姆·漢克斯獲頒總統自由勳章<ref>{{Cite web |first=Merrit |last=Kennedy |url=https://www.npr.org/sections/thetwo-way/2016/11/16/502347068/these-are-the-21-people-receiving-the-nations-highest-civilian-honor |title=These Are The 21 People Receiving The Nation's Highest Civilian Honor |publisher=NPR |date=2016-11-16 |accessdate=2016-11-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161116224356/http://www.npr.org/sections/thetwo-way/2016/11/16/502347068/these-are-the-21-people-receiving-the-nations-highest-civilian-honor |archive-date=2016-11-16 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 其他 ==
湯·漢斯支持[[同性婚姻|同性婚姻]]、環境議題以及[[替代燃料|替代燃料]]。亦為[[民主党_(美国)|民主党]]黨員，曾支持许多民主党[[政治人物|政治人物]]，包括[[贝拉克·奥巴马|贝拉克·奥巴马]]、[[希拉里·克林顿|希拉里·克林顿]]、[[乔·拜登|乔·拜登]]。

2020年3月12日，湯姆漢克斯透過[[Instagram|Instagram]]表示自己和妻子都確診[[2019冠状病毒病|2019冠状病毒病]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=汤姆·汉克斯夫妇感染新冠病毒|url=https://cn.nytimes.com/usa/20200312/tom-hanks-coronavirus/|accessdate=2020-08-04|date=2020-03-12|last=《纽约时报》2020年3月12日|work=纽约时报中文网|language=zh-hans|archive-date=2020-04-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200407034002/https://cn.nytimes.com/usa/20200312/tom-hanks-coronavirus/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，兩人當時在澳洲拍攝由[[巴茲·雷曼|巴茲·雷曼]]執導的電影《[[艾維斯_(電影)|艾維斯]]》<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2020/03/tom-hanks-rita-wilson-test-positive-coronavirus-elvis-presley-movie-1202880431/|title=Tom Hanks & Rita Wilson Test Positive For Coronavirus As Outbreak Hits ‘Elvis Presley’ Film|last=D'Alessandro|first=Anthony|last2=D'Alessandro|first2=Anthony|date=2020-03-12|website=Deadline|language=en|access-date=2020-03-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200312081419/https://deadline.com/2020/03/tom-hanks-rita-wilson-test-positive-coronavirus-elvis-presley-movie-1202880431/|archive-date=2020-03-12|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://variety.com/2020/film/news/tom-hanks-rita-wilson-coronavirus-1203531498/|title=Tom Hanks, Rita Wilson Test Positive for Coronavirus|last=Stedman|first=Alex|last2=Stedman|first2=Alex|date=2020-03-12|website=Variety|language=en|access-date=2020-03-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200312012152/https://variety.com/2020/film/news/tom-hanks-rita-wilson-coronavirus-1203531498/|archive-date=2020-03-12|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last1=Gonzalez |first1=Sandra |title=Tom Hanks and Rita Wilson diagnosed with coronavirus |url=https://www.cnn.com/2020/03/11/entertainment/tom-hanks-rita-wilson-coronavirus/index.html |website=CNN |accessdate=2020-03-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200312030049/https://www.cnn.com/2020/03/11/entertainment/tom-hanks-rita-wilson-coronavirus/index.html |archive-date=2020-03-12 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。3月16日，漢克斯夫妻出院<ref name="Hospitalrelease">{{cite news |last1=Melas |first1=Chloe |title=Tom Hanks and Rita Wilson released from the hospital following coronavirus diagnosis |url=https://amp.cnn.com/cnn/2020/03/16/entertainment/tom-hanks-rita-wilson-released-hospital-coronavirus/index.html |accessdate=2020-03-20 |agency=[[CNN_International|CNN International]] |date=2020-03-16 |archive-date=2020-12-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201229040903/https://amp.cnn.com/cnn/2020/03/16/entertainment/tom-hanks-rita-wilson-released-hospital-coronavirus/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，兩人結束隔離後，同月27日返回洛杉磯<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-health-coronavirus-hanks-idUSKBN21F00L|title=Tom Hanks returns to LA after bout of coronavirus: media reports|website=Reuters|date=2020-03-27|access-date=2020-03-28|archive-date=2020-12-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201229040842/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-health-coronavirus-hanks-idUSKBN21F00L|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

